sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as notebook-controller

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access

    User->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>No auth token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    Proxy->>OAuth: OAuth2 authentication flow<br/>HTTPS/443
    OAuth-->>Proxy: JWT Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward request (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups<br/>X-Forwarded-Access-Token
    Backend->>Backend: Serve static files<br/>(React SPA)
    Backend-->>Proxy: HTML/JS/CSS
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 2: API Request to Kubernetes

    User->>Route: GET /api/namespaces (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: User/Group/Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /api/v1/namespaces<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Namespace list (JSON)
    Backend-->>Proxy: API Response
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    User->>Route: GET /api/prometheus/* (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: User/Group/Token
    Backend->>Thanos: POST /api/v1/query<br/>HTTPS/9092<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics data (JSON)
    Backend-->>Proxy: API Response
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Metrics JSON

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 4: Notebook Creation

    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>Body: Notebook spec
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: User/Group/Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/namespaces/{ns}/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI->>NotebookCtrl: Notebook CR created (watch event)
    NotebookCtrl->>NotebookCtrl: Reconcile:<br/>Create Pod, Service, Route
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR (JSON)
    Backend-->>Proxy: API Response
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Notebook created confirmation
